description.en: ERC223 IS A NEW TOKEN THAT TAKES A DIFFERENT APPROACH, BY RELEASING THE TOKEN ONLY IN SATURN.NETWORK AND MAKING IT ITS OWN EXCHANGE, IT AVOIDS SPENDING DEVS FUNDS, ALLOWS THE LOWEST PRICE FOR HOLDERS, IS A PERFECT BUY AT THE LOWEST PRICE, WHILE BEING A BETTER VERSION OF ERC20, 95% OF TOKENS EXCLUDIVELY SOLD ONLY IN SATURN NETWORK.
